            <![CDATA[
<p> Please make sure it's thread-safe in multi-thread environment. Either make it immutable or make sure it is not reassigned after initialization</p>
]]>
        </Details>
    </BugPattern>

    <BugPattern type="ASSIGN_MUTABLE_STATIC_FIELD">
        <ShortDescription>Mutable Static Class.</ShortDescription>
        <LongDescription>
            Assigning values to static variables
